sections.heading: to 59A-3-9 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1998, ch. 108, § 81 repealed 59A-3-1 to 59A-3-9 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1984, ch. 127, §§ 35 to 44, relating to the state insurance board, effective January 1, 1999. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1997 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
